{"tid":786430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳浩天向特朗普發信　譚惠珠：有外國力量參與的民主運動結果都不理想","createTime":"2018-08-20T02:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T21:18:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"446d8e866040d5191dc76bf8aa068acc4942e18e","tid":786430,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180820/s00001/529ad4f5cebb4c307799ad094593d6d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180820%2Fs00001%2F529ad4f5cebb4c307799ad094593d6d9.jpg&h=a6aa00fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港民族黨召集人陳浩天日前向美國總統特朗普發公開信，稱鑑於香港自由迅速惡化，促請美國總統特朗普審視《美國&mdash;香港政策法》，並撤銷香港和中國的世界貿易組織成員身分。基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠接受港台節目訪問時，批評陳浩天行徑不但令自己更不利，更損害香港利益，又稱從過往例子來說，有外國力量參與的民主運動，結果都是不理想。<br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠指，她不少身邊人都直斥有關行徑過分，而她自己認為雖然爭取開明選舉制度無錯，但應靠自己人爭取，不應倚重外國力量。她稱從過往例子來說，有外國力量參與的民主運動，結果都是不理想。<br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠重申，香港不需要香港外國記者會（FCC）舉辦陳浩天演講來證明言論自由，因香港言論自由世界享譽，而且市民可隨意致電政府熱線表達不滿，加上沒有任何一間傳媒因報道港獨而被取締，因此FCC行徑多餘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180820/s00001/1534730366247\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180820%2Fs00001%2F1534730366247&d=4T8dbDUuPIXk%2FVoA3xnEsdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=1e2f6db2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180820%2Fs00001%2F1534730366247&h=df2890c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180820/s00001/1534730366247</a>"},{"pid":"3776c6d3ce708ecaed435705346ccdad9abc417c","tid":786430,"uid":44454,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:25:38.000Z","msg":"譚惠珠竟然希望發生理想的民主運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9650488a177e290af5f73bd9448599fde29dc15d","tid":786430,"uid":28759,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:26:26.000Z","msg":"是但啦<br />\n好似以巴咁攬炒都冇所謂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講起當年共慘黨咪又係靠蘇聯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bceba74291fbb3c4005f463d9bde6531afc00d26","tid":786430,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:26:34.000Z","msg":"陳浩天本身係英國人"},{"pid":"68f63bbf532ee60fd484beeb292f40dd956861f7","tid":786430,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3776c6d3ce708ecaed435705346ccdad9abc417c","tid":786430,"uid":44454,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:25:38.000Z","msg":"譚惠珠竟然希望發生理想的民主運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:26:42.000Z","msg":"還是毛主席式的民眾運動"},{"pid":"1ccbd34bedad42daefce730e417827c4ebc2b2a9","tid":786430,"uid":77803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd44d9823ed785e4b8dae6e1ee6fddc0da3adf05","tid":786430,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3776c6d3ce708ecaed435705346ccdad9abc417c","tid":786430,"uid":44454,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:25:38.000Z","msg":"譚惠珠竟然希望發生理想的民主運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:27:10.000Z","msg":"最理想係你有你嘈, 佢有佢日日殖民唔聽你講"},{"pid":"bb0ecb38ef328f46147f9a7a03801ed467edc99c","tid":786430,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:28:11.000Z","msg":"Up乜春民主運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5013915fc2a73dd5ca11415e4aeb95216dd